quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  1,1,"All praise is due to God, the Lord of the Universe"
  1,2,"the Beneficent, the Merciful"
  1,3,Lord of the Day of Judgement
  1,4,"You alone we worship, and to You alone we turn for help"
  1,5,Guide us to the straight path
  1,6,"the path of those You have blessed; not of those who have incurred Your wrath, nor of those who have gone astray"